	(text "Calcumaker 16 display — Interconnect to the main board. J1 pinout (MUST match calcumaker-main J3): 1=+3V3, 2=GND, 3=CLK (shared), 4=DIN1, 5=DIN2, 6=DIN3, 7=GND, 8=spare. (TM1640 2-wire: one shared CLK + one DIN per row driver U1/U2/U3.) Wide +3V3/GND for LED current. 2.54mm 1x8 header (C492407); short cable to the angled display. See DESIGN.md Board Partition."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
